import React from 'react'; const RulesPage = () => { return (

🏈 Welcome to the Shama-lama-ding-dong Football Challenge!

🕺 On behalf of Master Blaster and Alice in Chain’s
🎙️ “It’s good to be back at the Dexter Lake Club”
💜 “Otis, he loves us”
🎵 So hit it...

📩 Getting Started

  • 📧 Each player must have an email address and a game name
  • 💵 Pay $60 up front to play
  • 🧾 Total cost: $160.00
  • 💰 Payments due before Weeks 1, 6, and 11

🗓️ Season Timeline

  • 🏁 Starts: Thursday, August 29, 2019 {/* <-- EDIT THIS DATE WHEN READY */}
  • 🏁 Ends: Monday, December 16, 2019 {/* <-- EDIT THIS DATE WHEN READY */}
  • ✅ Covers 15 weeks of NCAA + NFL regular season (Week 14 NFL)

🎯 How to Play

  • ✅ Pick any mix of college/NFL games from Thursday to Monday
  • ✍️ Submit picks before Thursday’s first game kick-off
  • 📤 Use the spread we send out via email (Tuesday night or Wednesday morning)
  • 📜 Only pick from games on the sheet
  • 📋 Choose exactly 10 teams — only the first 10 will count
  • ✅ 1 point per win, 0 points per loss

🏆 How to Win

  • ⭐ Get 9 out of 10 right in a week = you win the pot
  • 🎁 No weekly winner? → the pot rolls over
  • 🤝 Multiple winners? → the pot is split evenly
  • 🏅 No winners for 15 weeks? → player with highest total points wins the pot
  • 🧠 Tie on points? → we check your #1 ranked CFP team pick
  • 🤷‍♂️ Still tied? → split the pot

🙅‍♂️ Other Notes

  • 🚫 Cancelled games still require 9 correct picks to win the pot
  • ⛔ Cancelled = 0 points (no reschedules allowed)
  • 🙋 This is a game — organizers receive no payment
  • ❤️ Winnings can be donated to the charity of your choice
); }; export default RulesPage;
